#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
BULLETPROOF PLAYER PROPS - ENHANCED FEATURE ENGINEERING
========================================================
68-72 features for ML model training and prediction

This mirrors the main model architecture with identical philosophy:
- Same feature categories as main 78-feature system
- Pre-computed features ready for 7-model ensemble
- Single source of truth for all props ML models

Feature Categories (70 total):
1. Player Stats Features (28) - Season averages, recent form, splits, trends
2. Matchup Features (22) - Opponent defense, pace, historical performance
3. Context Features (15) - Rest days, venue, game importance
4. Market Features (5) - Line analysis, implied probabilities

IMPORTANT: This file is BULLETPROOF. Do not simplify or rename.
"""

